28#ifndef QTQRCODE_HPP
29#define QTQRCODE_HPP
30
31#include <QByteArray>
32#include <QSharedDataPointer>
33
34#include "libqrencode/qrencode.h"
35
36class QtQrCodeData;
37
38class QtQrCode
39{
40public:
41 enum Proportion {
42 NormalProportion = 0,
43 MicroProportion = 1
44 };
45 enum EncodeMode {
46 DataMode = 0,
47 StringMode,
48 KanjiMode,
49 };
50 enum ErrorCorrectionLevel {
51 LowLevel = QR_ECLEVEL_L,
52 MediumLevel = QR_ECLEVEL_M,
53 QuartileLevel = QR_ECLEVEL_Q,
54 HighLevel = QR_ECLEVEL_H
55 };
56 QtQrCode(int version);
57 QtQrCode(QtQrCode::EncodeMode encodeMod);
58 QtQrCode(const QByteArray &data = "", int version = 0,
59 QtQrCode::EncodeMode encodeMode = StringMode,
60 QtQrCode::Proportion proportion = NormalProportion,
61 Qt::CaseSensitivity caseSensitivity = Qt::CaseSensitive,
62 QtQrCode::ErrorCorrectionLevel errorCorrectionLevel = LowLevel);
63 QtQrCode(const QtQrCode &);
64 QtQrCode &operator=(const QtQrCode &);
65 ~QtQrCode();
66
67 int width() const;
68
69 int version() const;
70 void setVersion(int version);
71
72 QByteArray data() const;
73 void setData(const QByteArray &data);
74
75 EncodeMode encodeMode() const;
76 void setEncodeMode(QtQrCode::EncodeMode encodeMode);
77
78 Proportion proportion() const;
79 void setProportion(QtQrCode::Proportion proportion);
80
81 Qt::CaseSensitivity caseSensitivity() const;
82 void setCaseSensitivity(Qt::CaseSensitivity caseSensitivity);
83
84 ErrorCorrectionLevel errorCorrectionLevel() const;
85 void setErrorCorrectionLevel(QtQrCode::ErrorCorrectionLevel errorCorrectionLevel);
86
87 bool operator ==(const QtQrCode &other);
88 bool operator !=(const QtQrCode &other);
89
90protected:
91 QSharedDataPointer<QtQrCodeData> d;
92 void encode();
93private:
94 void constructorPrivate(const QByteArray &data = "", int version = 0,
95 QtQrCode::EncodeMode encodeMode = StringMode,
96 QtQrCode::Proportion proportion = NormalProportion,
97 Qt::CaseSensitivity caseSensitivity = Qt::CaseSensitive,
98 QtQrCode::ErrorCorrectionLevel errorCorrectionLevel = LowLevel);
99 void setBaseQrCodeData(QRcode *qrCode);
100 void encodeData();
101 void encodeString();
102 void encodeSKanji();
103};
104
105#endif // QTQRCODE_HPP
